parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof can cause injuries from flying glass, distractions while driving, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Loud explosion or gunshot-like sound
shattered glass falling into the vehicle
glass shards on the driver and passengers
and potential injuries from cuts or abrasions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering coupler can cause the steering wheel to malfunction, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential harm to drivers and passengers.
symptoms: Clicking or thudding noise when turning the steering wheel
excessive play or looseness in the steering wheel
vibration while driving
and difficulty controlling the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience intermittent issues, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the engine light comes on
the radio and backup camera become inoperable
the push-to-start button fails to start the vehicle
and the vehicle experiences intermittent starting issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience intermittent issues, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the HVAC and blower motor can cause a fire hazard, burning plastic smell, and melting of the wiring harness.
symptoms: The AC control unit fails
the AC fan stops working
the AC control knob makes a grinding noise
the wiring harness connected to the backside of the AC control knob melts and deforms
the AC only works in certain positions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the safety and visibility features can cause accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The rear seat belts and passenger airbags fail
the rear seat belts cannot be released from the seat or retracted
the airbag warning light remains illuminated
the anti-theft unit activates independently
the tail pipe releases a black powder.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Loud knocking or rattling noise from the engine
loss of power
engine stalling
smoke coming from the engine
oil leaks
and check engine light illumination.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor
clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive oil consumption and leaks can cause engine damage, leading to engine failure and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: Oil light illumination
low oil levels
oil leaks
and burning oil smell.
